f="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-boasts-17000-possible-endings-3469777">的结局有 17,000 种变化</a>，以反映玩家在叙事中选择的水平。该游戏还允许平衡和战术家难度级别的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/baldurs-gate-3-mod-allows-multiclassing-on-its-easiest-difficulty-3478239">多重职业</a>，激发更多的个人表达。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/the-pokemon-company">神奇宝贝公司</a>宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/pokemon-presents-livestream-announced-for-next-week-with-glitchy-teaser-3478400">下周将有一场神奇宝贝礼物直播</a>，但不同的标志激起了人们的好奇心。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/critical-role-star-matthew-mercer-takes-on-baldurs-gate-3-castle-with-boxes-3478424">观看《关键角色》后，明星马修·默瑟 (Matthew Mercer) 使用 45 个板条箱潜入《博德之门 3》中的城堡，</a>率先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
